== 回響 ==
=== 評論 ===
英國知名電影評論網站[[Eye_For_Film|Eye For Film]]的Amber Wilkinson給與四顆星的評價(滿分五顆星)，並且稱讚音樂的部分「歌曲和舞蹈的數量處理得宜並且朗朗上口，沒有比它們更好的」(the song and dance numbers are so well-handled and catchy, it's a shame there aren't more of them.)。然而，她也說「角色過於單薄以至於就像是沒有一般("characters are so wafer thin they barely cast a shadow.")<!-- Spelling error in source is trivial; per guidelines, correct quietly --><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eyeforfilm.co.uk/reviews.php?film_id=15319 |title=Another Cinderella Story Movie Review (2008)|work=[[Eye_For_Film|Eye For Film]]|access-date=2012-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120407031802/http://www.eyeforfilm.co.uk/reviews.php?film_id=15319|archive-date=2012-04-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 評論家Lacey Walker則指出許多與[[灰姑娘的玻璃手機|灰姑娘的玻璃手機]]過於類似之處，並給了三顆星。Lacey Walker則稱讚劇本並表示編劇「充分表現幽默並有許多趣味橋段」(peppered this story with a surprising dose of humor and some pleasing plot twists.)但是Lacey Walker也具體指出15歲的賽琳娜和25歲的朱兒差別過於明顯(glaringly obvious)。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.christiananswers.net/spotlight/movies/2008/anothercinderellastory2008.html|title=Another Cinderella Story Movie Review|publisher=christiananswers.net|access-date=2012-01-24|archive-date=2019-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115232447/https://christiananswers.net/spotlight/movies/2008/anothercinderellastory2008.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 收視率 ==
[[ABC_Family|ABC Family]]電視台在2009年1月18日首播本電影。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcfamily.go.com/abcfamily/path/section_Movies+Another-Cinderella-Story/page_Detail|title=ABC Family: Selena Gomez and Drew Seely in Another Cinderella Story|publisher=ABC.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100620064020/http://abcfamily.go.com/abcfamily/path/section_Movies+Another-Cinderella-Story/page_Detail|archivedate=2010年6月20日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>獲得530萬的觀眾人數。在2009年1月的有線電視當中獲得收視冠軍。成人18-34歲(100萬)、成人18-49歲(190萬)，12-34歲的觀眾群(230萬)。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/b80120_battlestar_galactica_flies_high_tween.html |title=Battlestar Galactica Flies High, Tween Shows Fly Higher |publisher=[[E!_Online|E! Online]] |access-date=2012-01-24 |archive-date=2009-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090626062509/http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/b80120_battlestar_galactica_flies_high_tween.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>(美國尼爾森媒體調查；調查時間：2008/12/29~2009/01/25) 

